{% section headline="Sections - Nunjucks Component", headingLevel="3" -%}
    <p>Sections should wrap parts of content that have a headline. It enforces rules for basic page layout and line-lengths.</p>

<pre><code>&lbrace;% section headline='Headline goes here' %&rbrace;
  HTML for whatever goes in this section
&lbrace;%- endsection %&rbrace;</code></pre>


    <p>By default headlines have an h2 tag, to change it with the <code>headingLevel</code> flag</p>

    <pre><code>&lbrace;% section headline="Headline goes here",
    headingLevel="3"
 %&rbrace;
  HTML for whatever goes in this section
&lbrace;%- endsection %&rbrace;</code></pre>

  {%- endsection %}


